      value: 'Pingalaka banished all jackals from the forest. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[10].option2
      value: '...their tails were not fuffly anymore. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[10].option3
      value: '...they lost all privileges. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[10].option4
      value: "...they didn\u2019t get enough food to eat."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[0].questionText
      value: '1. In which town did Danila the merchant live? '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[1].questionText
      value: '2. What was the king''s servant name? '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[2].questionText
      value: '3. How did Dantila feel when Gorambha accidentally sat on the seat
        meant for noble people? '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[3].questionText
      value: '4. When Gorambha was kicked out of the building he... '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[4].questionText
      value: '5. Gorambha told the king that he was ..... all night and had no sleep
        at all. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[5].questionText
      value: '6. We should never think of anyone as insignificant or too low because... '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[6].questionText
      value: '7. Later in the story, Dantila invited Gorambha to his house with the
        intention of... '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[7].questionText
      value: '8. Simple gestures go a long way in making people... '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[8].questionText
      value: '9. When Pingalaka met Sanjaka for the first time.. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8708457752166727022, guid: a2c7304e82d0653459caddc8bd40338b, type: 3}
      propertyPath: questions.Array.data[9].questionText
      value: '10. By spending more time with Sanjivaka, Pingalaka became... (Select
        all answers that are correct) '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
